= One-Page game pitch --- Katana

== Raid
We play tested our main gameplay loop: combat an found some good findings. First we tested to play on a map that had many narrow streets. See figures 1-3.
We thought it was a bit to tight streets on the first map we did. When we play tested we found out that if many enemies attacked the player would like to have more of an open space.
So we changed the map to include this. (See figure 4-5)

